00:25:30,310 --> 00:25:31,110
Good morning, Siyue.

444
00:25:31,400 --> 00:25:31,950
Morning.

445
00:25:43,070 --> 00:25:44,000
What's up?

446
00:25:44,800 --> 00:25:46,000
Zhou Siyue

