00:25:47,680 --> 00:25:48,710
Breakfast.

448
00:25:50,350 --> 00:25:51,430
Marinated Eggs again?

449
00:25:52,110 --> 00:25:53,110
Really?

450
00:25:55,110 --> 00:25:56,590
